summary: A collection of stories by Maharg67 made manifest in game.
descriptionHtml:
A collection of stories put into book format in the game. The stories are by Maharg67 and are not my own work, but he has given me permission to publish
this mod.

The books can be found in Whiterun as soon as you enter turn left and maharg is standing/sitting on a balcony surrounded by his books. He will throw the occasional insult at you.

Enjoy!

Credits:

Mod by JediJas

Stories by Maharg67

Don\'t forget to endorse, comment and visit my website:

http://www.jedijas.com
author: jedijas
